{
  "stem": "868.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The need to blend in, to be part of the others, was never granted to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although I did make some, some friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then what happened?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, well, from 1936 until 1939, it was easier to be a foreigner, a refugee, a Jew, in, in Paris.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1939, the war started officially-- September 1, 1939, when France and England declared war on Germany after they attacked Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the effects of the war were not felt in, in, in Paris for a long time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had an expression for it called 'drole de guerre,' which means a funny kind of war, because nothing happened, not on the French front.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans were busy in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm not sure exactly when.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I believe April, 1940, they started paying attention to the Western Front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's when they started invading Belgium, Holland, Luxembourg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, of course, the war came closer to France itself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember any air raids, nothing, until June, 1940.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's when they entered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After having conquered Luxembourg, Holland, and Belgium, they entered the French territory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we still felt kind of cocky about it, because there was the Maginot Line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever heard of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "M-A-G-I-N-O-T, which was a superb engineering achievement-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a fortification line that extended all the way from the German border [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the way across to Belgium and was supposed to be impregnable.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They continually showed pictures of how deep the bunkers were and all these corridors and how everything was geared to repulse any, any attack.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The fact is that the Germans took it in something like 24 hours by not even attacking it.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
